Package: wordcloud.mappeR
Type: Package
Title: A package for creating wordcloud maps in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person('Lorenzo', 'Gini', role = "aut"),
    person('Julian', 'Kath', role = "aut"),
    person('Gabriel', 'da Silva Zech', role = c("aut","cre"))
    )
Maintainer: Gabriel da Silva Zech <gabrielszech@gmail.com>
Description: A package that allows one to create wordclouds shaped like regions in a map. 
    It relies on 'giscoR' for retreiving the shapes of regions and 'ggwordcloud' for creating the wordclouds.
    The classification of regions is based on the European Union's NUTS geocode standard.
